<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.5">
<l>mattaḷa vuntayirum vārkuḻal naṉmaṭavār</l>
<l rend="indent">vaittaṉa neykaḷavāl vārivi ḻuṅkiyoruṅ</l>
<l>kottavi ṇaimaruta muṉṉiya vantavarai</l>
<l rend="indent">yūruka rattiṉoṭu muntiya ventiṟalōy</l>
<l>muttiṉi ḷamuṟuval muṟṟava ruvataṉmuṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">muṉṉamu kattaṇiyār moykuḻal kaḷalaiya</l>
<l>vattave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having taken by the handful with trickery,</l>
<l rend="indent">[you] totally devoured the ghee that was kept by the good women</l>
<l>with long, curling hair, along with the curds</l>
<l rend="indent">that measured [as high as] the churning rod,</l>
<l>You who has great strength who opposed with thighs and hands</l>
<l rend="indent">those who emerged from the identical twin Marutam [trees]!</l>
<l>So that [your] beautiful thick curls sway to and fro in front of [your] face</l>
<l rend="indent">[with] young, pearl [like] teeth before becoming fully grown,</l>
<l>O Father, dance one time for me!</l>
<l rend="indent">Battle bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
